  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Any adult (18 years of age or older) patient eligible for a bone anchored hearing
             system

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Inability or unwillingness to participate in follow-up

          -  Skin thickness of &gt; 10 mm

          -  Diseases known to compromise bone quality

          -  Irradiated in the implant area
      </textblock>
